output_list.impact: Integer overflow in mintToken function allows the owner to set the balance of an arbitrary user to any value.
freezeAccount function allows the owner to freeze the account of any user, which removes the owner's only access control mechanism.
setPrices function is public, allowing any user to change the prices used to buy and sell tokens.
Integer overflow in buy function allows the owner to set the balance of the buyer to any value.
Integer overflow in sell function allows the owner to set the balance of the seller to any value.
Integer overflow in setBalance function allows the owner to set the balance of an arbitrary user to any value.
toOwner function is public, allowing any user to change the owner of the contract.
destruct function is public, allowing any user to destroy the contract.
